Linux client is written in vala language using webkit-gtk library.

Build instructions.

In order to build the program you should install it's dependencies first:

$ sudo apt-get install valac-0.16, build-essential, libgtk2.0-dev, libwebkitgtk-dev

Packages are for latest ubuntu distribution.

To build just type `make`.

If you want to specify install target you may want to redefine INSTALL_PREFIX variable,
which equals to `./bundle` by default

`make INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local`
